Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.97,0:02:38.35,Shinsou main,TSUBAKI,0000,0000,0000,,{Sorry.}Promiň.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.35,0:02:42.01,Shinsou main,TSUBAKI,0000,0000,0000,,{Akira's the only one who \Nended up joining the cause.}Nakonec je Akira jediná kdo se připojil.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.23,0:02:45.14,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{I appreciate the help.}Oceňuji tvou pomoc.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.59,0:02:48.27,Shinsou main,AKIRA,0000,0000,0000,,{You really know what\N the Foundation's goals are?}Opravdu víte jaké jsou cíle nadace?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.53,0:02:52.43,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{Yeah, thanks to Kurokami-san\N and Kakihara-san.}Jo, díky Kurokami a panu Kakiharovi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.82,0:02:54.95,Shinsou main,TSUBAKI,0000,0000,0000,,{I can't believe Kakihara's dead, too.}Nemůžu uvěřit, že je Kakihara taky mrtvý.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.44,0:02:59.65,Shinsou main,KOTETSU,0000,0000,0000,,{I always thought he was horrible for\N attacking Chihiro-san so aggressively.}Myslel jsem si, že byl strašný když se choval tak hrozně k Chihirovi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.18,0:03:02.91,Shinsou main,KOTETSU,0000,0000,0000,,{It's not fair that he ended\N up being a good guy.}Není fér, že skončil když se zrovna stával dobrým.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.67,0:03:05.44,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{Our fight's not over.}Náš boj ještě není u konce.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.16,0:03:09.29,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{They've left it up to us}Nechali to na nás
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.14,0:03:14.16,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{to stop Chaos' plans and \Nsurvive, no matter what.}zastavit Chaosův plán a přežít, jedno jak.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.79,0:03:20.16,Shinsou main,SHOKO,0000,0000,0000,,{I'm surprised a member of the Guardian\N State wants to work with us.}Byla jsem překvapena, když jedna ze strážkyň chtěla pomoci.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.11,0:03:25.55,Shinsou main,SHOKO,0000,0000,0000,,{After what happened to Kurokami\NMarie-san, I thought they'd had enough.}Potom co se stalo Kurokami Marii jsem myslela, že mají dost.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.46,0:03:28.76,Shinsou main,KOTETSU,0000,0000,0000,,{This is no time to be saying that.}Teď není čas takhle mluvit.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.76,0:03:31.89,Shinsou main,TSUBAKI,0000,0000,0000,,{Marie acted of her own volition.}Marie jednala z vlastní vůle.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.89,0:03:33.74,Shinsou main,TSUBAKI,0000,0000,0000,,{So do we.}Tak to děláme.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.18,0:03:36.40,Shinsou main,AKIRA,0000,0000,0000,,{It has nothing to do with the Guardian State.}Nemá to co dělat se strážci.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.02,0:03:39.96,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{Right now we need all the people we can get.}Popravdě potřebujeme všechny lidi, které můžeme sehnat.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.83,0:03:42.05,Shinsou main,DUX,0000,0000,0000,,{I'm sure you do}Tomu věřím
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.96,0:03:49.37,Shinsou main,DUX,0000,0000,0000,,{The six installed machines are\Nprojecting barriers around each other.}Šest nainstalovaných zařízení mezi sebou vytváří bariéry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.37,0:03:51.37,Shinsou main,DUX,0000,0000,0000,,{It's impossible to destroy them.}Je nemožné je zničit.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.10,0:03:56.77,Shinsou main,DUX,0000,0000,0000,,{When this Big Dipper is completed, \Nthe Second Great Collapse will occur.}Jakmile bude Velký vůz dokončen, nastane druhé Velké zhroucení.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.52,0:04:00.76,Shinsou main,DUX,0000,0000,0000,,{Your chances of survival\Nwill be practically zero.}Vaše šance na přežití jsou takřka nulové.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.74,0:04:04.81,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{We just have to stop them before \Nthey connect the last one.}Musíme to prostě zastavit než se spojí s posledním.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.87,0:04:08.46,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{According to the info\N Kakihara-san left me,}Podle informací, které mi pan Kakihara zanechal,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.10,0:04:13.07,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{the last one will be at the recently\Ncompleted Infinity Theater.}poslední z nich bude v nedávno dokončeném Nekonečném divadle.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.68,0:04:17.22,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{It was built by the AVAL Science Foundation.}Bylo postaveno Vědeckou nadací AVAL.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.22,0:04:18.83,Shinsou main,TSUBAKI,0000,0000,0000,,{It must be there.}Musí to být tam.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.78,0:04:24.63,Shinsou main,SHOKO,0000,0000,0000,,{Kakihara-san finally did\N something useful in the very end.}Kakihara nakonec udělal něco užitečného.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.12,0:04:26.83,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{What's so funny?}Co je tak k smíchu?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.83,0:04:30.66,Shinsou main,SHOKO,0000,0000,0000,,{Oh, I thought you'd be happy.}Ale, myslela jsem, že budeš rád.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.23,0:04:35.45,Shinsou main,SHOKO,0000,0000,0000,,{The thorn in your side who kept\N digging through your past is gone.}Trn v patě, který tě neustále tlačil do minulosti je pryč.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.45,0:04:36.42,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{Don't.}Přestaň.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.75,0:04:39.92,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{Kakihara-san told me to live.}Pan Kakihara mi řekl, abych žil.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.78,0:04:42.49,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{Like Inuki-san.}Jako Inuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.88,0:04:46.05,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{I will fulfill their wish.}Splním jejich přání.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.38,0:04:48.94,Shinsou main,SHOKO,0000,0000,0000,,{How magnificent.}Jak skvělé.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.94,0:04:52.68,Shinsou main,SHOKO,0000,0000,0000,,{I'm sure you can swing your\N blade without hesitation}Jsem si jistá, že se dokážeš ohánět čepelí bez váhání
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.27,0:04:57.02,Shinsou main,SHOKO,0000,0000,0000,,{even if Shiraki Yuri is among your enemies.}i když Shiraki Yuri je mezi tvými nepřáteli
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.65,0:05:03.64,Shinsou main,TSUBAKI,0000,0000,0000,,{What an unpleasant woman.}Jaká nepříjemná žena.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.64,0:05:04.84,Shinsou main,KOTETSU,0000,0000,0000,,{Chihiro-san.}Chihiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.13,0:05:07.27,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{I won't give up.}Nevzdám se.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.27,0:05:10.44,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{I'll change fate with my own hands.}Změním osud svýma vlastníma rukama.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.11,0:05:17.12,Shinsou main,GRUMMAN,0000,0000,0000,,{The time has come to cause\N the Second Great Collapse.}Nastal čas způsobit Druhé velké zhroucení.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.39,0:05:21.91,Shinsou main,GRUMMAN,0000,0000,0000,,{Though we've adopted an infallible\N plan centered around Kark,}I když jsme souhlasili s neomylným plánem zaměřující se na Karka,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.91,0:05:23.13,Shinsou main,GRUMMAN,0000,0000,0000,,{we can't let our guard down.}nesmíme polevit v ostražitosti.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.02,0:05:25.26,Shinsou main,JUN,0000,0000,0000,,{The final battle, huh?}Konečná bitva co?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.76,0:05:27.50,Shinsou main,JUN,0000,0000,0000,,{What will we be doing with Yuri?}Co uděláme s Yuri?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.50,0:05:29.97,Shinsou main,GRUMMAN,0000,0000,0000,,{She's useless.}Je k ničemu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.97,0:05:32.64,Shinsou main,DRAYLE,0000,0000,0000,,{We've got someone else who isn't doing anything.}Máme někoho jiného kdo nic nedělá.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.08,0:05:35.07,Shinsou main,DRAYLE,0000,0000,0000,,{Saving their strength?}Šetří své síly?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.75,0:05:39.69,Shinsou main,DRAYLE,0000,0000,0000,,{What if they turn out to be even\N more useless than Yuri?}Co když se ukáží, že jsou ještě neužitečnější než Yuri?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.02,0:05:42.39,Shinsou main,GRUMMAN,0000,0000,0000,,{Chiyu is my masterpiece.}Chiyu je mé mistrovské dílo.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.25,0:05:44.78,Shinsou main,GRUMMAN,0000,0000,0000,,{Don't compare them to Yuri.}Neporovnávej ji s Yuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.78,0:05:46.76,Shinsou main,DRAYLE,0000,0000,0000,,{Wow, scary.}Páni, děsivý.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.00,0:05:49.78,Shinsou main,JUN,0000,0000,0000,,{Even your own daughter, huh?}Dokonce i vaše vlastní dcera, co?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.78,0:05:51.00,Shinsou main,GRUMMAN,0000,0000,0000,,{What?}Cože?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.00,0:05:56.05,Shinsou main,JUN,0000,0000,0000,,{Is that how you abandoned your \Nexperimental subjects, too?}Taky jste opustil své pokusné králíky?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.65,0:05:57.79,Shinsou main,GRUMMAN,0000,0000,0000,,{My subjects?}Mé pokusné králíky?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.16,0:06:02.29,Shinsou main,GRUMMAN,0000,0000,0000,,{I don't remember my failures.}Nepamatuji si na své selhání.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.07,0:06:08.59,Shinsou main,GRUMMAN,0000,0000,0000,,{If you don't want to be scrapped,\N you'd best show me how useful you are.}Pokud nechceš být odstraněn, ukaž mi, že k něčemu jsi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.18,0:06:10.50,Shinsou main,JUN,0000,0000,0000,,{Of course.}Jistě.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.50,0:06:12.14,Shinsou main,JUN,0000,0000,0000,,{This time I'll kill Kamina Chihiro.}Tentokrát zabiju Kamina Chihiru.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.14,0:06:14.77,Shinsou main,GRUMMAN,0000,0000,0000,,{You'll be defending the other six locations.}Budeš bránit ostatních šest lokací.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.77,0:06:16.35,Shinsou main,JUN,0000,0000,0000,,{That's absurd!}To je absurdní.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.35,0:06:20.65,Shinsou main,JUN,0000,0000,0000,,{If they're trying to destroy the last one,\N Kamina Chihiro will surely be there!}Pokud chtějí zničit poslední, Kamina Chihiro se tam určitě ukáže!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.97,0:06:23.80,Shinsou main,JUN,0000,0000,0000,,{Why are you doing this to me again?}Proč mi to zase děláte?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.40,0:06:25.66,Shinsou main,JUN,0000,0000,0000,,{I won't accept this!}To nepřijmu!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.20,0:06:27.86,Shinsou main,DRAYLE,0000,0000,0000,,{You don't get it.}Nechápeš to.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.32,0:06:30.34,Shinsou main,DRAYLE,0000,0000,0000,,{That's why.}To je proč.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.82,0:06:37.87,Shinsou main,DRAYLE,0000,0000,0000,,{One of us might ignore the artificial\N keystone to get his revenge.}Jeden z nás by mohl ignorovat umělý klíč, aby se pomstil.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.28,0:06:40.75,Shinsou main,GRUMMAN,0000,0000,0000,,{My decisions are final.}Moje rozhodnutí je konečné.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.46,0:06:45.40,Shinsou main,HARU,0000,0000,0000,,{Wait, Jun-san!}Počkej, June!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.63,0:06:53.18,Shinsou main,JUN,0000,0000,0000,,{That may have been my only chance.}To byla možná moje jediná šance.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.54,0:06:57.29,Shinsou main,JUN,0000,0000,0000,,{I should've killed you.}Měl jsem tě zabít.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.67,0:07:00.64,Shinsou main,JUN,0000,0000,0000,,{Then I could've killed Kamina Chihiro.}Potom bych mohl zabít Kamina Chihiru.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.18,0:07:05.13,Shinsou main,JUN,0000,0000,0000,,{It's all because I was weak.}To vše, protože jsem byl slabý.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.42,0:07:07.38,Shinsou main,HARU,0000,0000,0000,,{Jun-san!}June!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.38,0:07:08.56,Shinsou main,JUN,0000,0000,0000,,{Don't follow me.}Nesleduj mě.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.93,0:07:13.99,Shinsou main,HARU,0000,0000,0000,,{This is your fault!}Je to tvá chyba!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.46,0:07:16.60,Shinsou main,HARU,0000,0000,0000,,{You've been talking to Kamina Chihiro, right?}Mluvila jsi s Kamino Chihirem, že?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.60,0:07:19.62,Shinsou main,HARU,0000,0000,0000,,{Lure him out so Jun-san can kill him, then!}Vylákej ho ven, tak aby ho mohl Jun zabít!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.62,0:07:21.12,Shinsou main,YURI,0000,0000,0000,,{I-I can't.}J-Já nemůžu.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.53,0:07:23.13,Shinsou main,HARU,0000,0000,0000,,{Don't you feel bad for Jun-san?}Necítíš se špatně kvůli Junovi?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.50,0:07:25.43,Shinsou main,HARU,0000,0000,0000,,{He's not happy with the situation!}Není spokojený s touhle situací.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.72,0:07:40.20,Shinsou main,TSUBAKI,0000,0000,0000,,{Kid.}Děcko.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.98,0:07:44.00,Shinsou main,TSUBAKI,0000,0000,0000,,{Pretty bold of you to come here alone.}Docela odvážný od tebe, že jsi přišel sám.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.48,0:07:49.23,Shinsou main,TSUBAKI,0000,0000,0000,,{What's his deal?}Co s ním je?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.04,0:07:53.24,Shinsou main,KOTETSU,0000,0000,0000,,{What's going on?}Co se děje?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.24,0:07:57.62,sign_11347_106_Special_Performa,,0000,0000,0000,,{Special Performance}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.47,0:07:57.62,Shinsou main,SHOKO,0000,0000,0000,,{On this day, they're transporting \Nthe artificial keystone.}V tento den převáží umělý klíč.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.00,0:07:58.91,Shinsou main,SHOKO,0000,0000,0000,,{Or perhaps...}Nebo snad ...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.43,0:08:02.04,Shinsou main,TSUBAKI,0000,0000,0000,,{They're causing the Second Great Collapse.}Se snaží vyvolat Druhé velké zhroucení.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.04,0:08:03.26,Shinsou main,KOTETSU,0000,0000,0000,,{That's not good.}To není dobrý.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.76,0:08:07.63,Shinsou main,KOUME,0000,0000,0000,,{But he went out of his way to tell us.}Ale vyšel ven jen aby nám to řekl.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.63,0:08:09.85,Shinsou main,SHOKO,0000,0000,0000,,{It must be a trap.}Musí to být past.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.74,0:08:12.81,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{Maybe they're issuing a challenge.}Možná to představuje výzvu.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.27,0:08:15.55,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{"Stop us if you can."}Zastav nás jestli to dokážeš.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.55,0:08:17.71,Shinsou main,TSUBAKI,0000,0000,0000,,{They underestimate us.}Podceňují nás.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.71,0:08:19.45,Shinsou main,KOTETSU,0000,0000,0000,,{Let's get them, Chihiro-san.}Jdem na ně, Chihiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.94,0:08:21.52,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{It's not that simple.}To není tak jednoduché
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.52,0:08:22.91,Shinsou main,AKIRA,0000,0000,0000,,{Why not?}Proč ne?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.91,0:08:24.22,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{It's a concert.}Je to koncert.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.73,0:08:27.02,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{There will be a lot of \Npeople in the audience.}V publiku bude hodně lidí.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.29,0:08:28.77,Shinsou main,KOUME,0000,0000,0000,,{You mean, they're...}Myslíš si, že jsou...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.35,0:08:31.62,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{They're all hostages.}Jsou všichni rukojmí.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.62,0:08:35.47,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{If we charge in there, they won't hesitate\N to turn all of them into monsters.}Jestli tam nakráčíme, promění všechny v monstra.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.47,0:08:37.06,Shinsou main,KOTETSU,0000,0000,0000,,{How cruel.}Kruté.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.06,0:08:39.16,Shinsou main,SHOKO,0000,0000,0000,,{If the Second Great Collapse occurs,}Pokud vyvolají Druhé velké zhroucení,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.46,0:08:43.04,Shinsou main,SHOKO,0000,0000,0000,,{Tokyo will be turned into\N a hell swirling with evil spirits.}Tokio bude proměněno v peklo, které se bude hemžit zlými duchy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.84,0:08:45.67,Shinsou main,SHOKO,0000,0000,0000,,{We can't avoid making some sacrifices.}Nemůžeme se vyvarovat některých obětí.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.67,0:08:48.39,Shinsou main,TSUBAKI,0000,0000,0000,,{How can you say that so casually?}Jak to můžeš říct tak lehce?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.39,0:08:49.53,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{Let's go.}Jdem.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.04,0:08:51.30,Shinsou main,TSUBAKI,0000,0000,0000,,{You serious?}Jsi si jistý?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.30,0:08:53.34,Shinsou main,KOTETSU,0000,0000,0000,,{But, the hostages...}Ale, ty rukojmí...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.34,0:08:55.50,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{They use some kind of sound...}Používají nějaký zvuk...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.92,0:08:58.76,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{Some kind of resonance\N to transform people.}Nějaký druh rozonance k přeměně lidí.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.32,0:09:04.17,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{With a full house, they'll most\N likely use Kark's piano music.}S plnou budovou s největší pravděpodobností využijí Karkovu klavírní hudbu.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.81,0:09:07.66,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{If we take him out before he can play...}Pokud bychom ho dostali pryč než začne hrát...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.69,0:09:11.07,Shinsou main,TSUBAKI,0000,0000,0000,,{I see. Great idea, Chihi.}Chápu. Skvělý nápad, Chichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.07,0:09:12.42,Shinsou main,KOTETSU,0000,0000,0000,,{That would work.}To by mohlo fungovat.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.01,0:09:22.90,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{There's no other way.}Není jiné cesty.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.90,0:09:26.42,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{One mistake, and many will die.}Jedna chyba a mnoho lidí umře.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.46,0:09:31.02,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{What can I do?}Co můžu udělat?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.16,0:09:40.99,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{Is this the answer?}To je odpověď?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.99,0:09:43.40,Shinsou main,DUX,0000,0000,0000,,{Who will die next?}Kdo umře další?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.40,0:09:45.72,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{You can even appear in people's dreams?}Můžeš se dokonce objevit ve snech lidí?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.30,0:09:48.43,Shinsou main,DUX,0000,0000,0000,,{Dreams?}Snech?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.43,0:09:50.53,Shinsou main,DUX,0000,0000,0000,,{You still don't understand.}Stále nechápeš.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.53,0:09:51.86,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{What do you mean?}Co tím myslíš?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.80,0:09:56.30,Shinsou main,DUX,0000,0000,0000,,{You thought you could change fate,}Myslel sis, že bys mohl změnit osud,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.30,0:09:59.35,Shinsou main,DUX,0000,0000,0000,,{but Kurokami Marie and\N Kakihara Isshin have vanished.}ale Kurokami Marie a Kakihara Isshin zmizely.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.16,0:10:02.60,Shinsou main,DUX,0000,0000,0000,,{Expectations are the cause of all suffering.}Očekávání jsou příčinou veškerého utrpení.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.60,0:10:04.44,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{I'm not giving up.}Nevzdávám se.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.00,0:10:06.64,Shinsou main,DUX,0000,0000,0000,,{Will killing Kark solve your problem?}Zabitím Karka se vyřeší tvůj problém?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.51,0:10:10.91,Shinsou main,DUX,0000,0000,0000,,{For the first time, you have a pure\Ndesire the death of an individual.}Poprvé toužíš po smrti jednotlivce.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.75,0:10:13.32,Shinsou main,DUX,0000,0000,0000,,{That is murderous intent.}To je vražedný záměr.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.11,0:10:18.75,Shinsou main,DUX,0000,0000,0000,,{And you used to find staining your hands\N with blood more repugnant than anything.}A zvykl sis ušpinit ruce krví víc než cokoliv jiného.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.34,0:10:22.13,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{I won't ask for forgiveness.}Nebudu prosit o odpuštění.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.13,0:10:25.87,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{If I'm going to stain my hands with\Nblood, I'll do it of my own volition.}Pokus si budu špinit ruce krví, udělám to ze své vlastní vůle.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.62,0:10:28.94,Shinsou main,DUX,0000,0000,0000,,{You're different this time.}Jsi tentokrát jinný.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.44,0:10:36.46,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{I'm not afraid anymore.}Už se nebojím.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.07,0:10:40.53,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{I can do it.}Dokážu to.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.80,0:11:01.18,Shinsou main,JUN,0000,0000,0000,,{What are you doing here?}Co tu děláš?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.53,0:11:05.09,Shinsou main,HARU,0000,0000,0000,,{It's not like you to rot away out here.}To se ti nepodobá hnít tady.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.89,0:11:07.16,Shinsou main,JUN,0000,0000,0000,,{Go back to your post.}Vrať se na své stanoviště.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.16,0:11:09.31,Shinsou main,JUN,0000,0000,0000,,{They'll kill you if you ignore your orders.}Řekli, že tě zabijou pokud neuposlechneš rozkazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.64,0:11:12.20,Shinsou main,HARU,0000,0000,0000,,{Kamina Chihiro is coming tonight.}Kamina Chihiro dnes večer přijde.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.40,0:11:15.12,Shinsou main,HARU,0000,0000,0000,,{I told them.}Řekl jsem mu to.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.12,0:11:16.22,Shinsou main,JUN,0000,0000,0000,,{You idiot.}Blbe.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.22,0:11:20.10,Shinsou main,HARU,0000,0000,0000,,{But at this rate, you won't\N be yourself anymore!}Ale tímhle tempem už nebudeš sám sebou!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.97,0:11:22.95,Shinsou main,JUN,0000,0000,0000,,{Leave.}Odejdi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.52,0:11:26.10,Shinsou main,HARU,0000,0000,0000,,{I believe in you.}Já v tebe věřím.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.73,0:11:34.21,Shinsou main,BLUE F,0000,0000,0000,,{It's starting soon.}Začíná to brzo.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.62,0:11:35.89,Shinsou main,BLUE F,0000,0000,0000,,{Everything look good?}Vypadá všechno dobře?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.48,0:11:38.35,Shinsou main,BLUE G,0000,0000,0000,,{Everyone's inside, right?}Všichni jsou uvnitř, co?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.35,0:11:40.20,Shinsou main,BLUE E,0000,0000,0000,,{Let's go inside and listen.}Pojďme dovnitř si to poslechnout.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.20,0:11:43.14,Shinsou main,BLUE F,0000,0000,0000,,{You idiot. Jun-san's not here.}Blbe. Není tady Jun.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.14,0:11:44.48,Shinsou main,BLUE F,0000,0000,0000,,{We need to—}Musíme—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.53,0:11:46.52,Shinsou main,BLUE F,0000,0000,0000,,{What's that?}Co to je?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.82,0:11:49.52,Shinsou main,BLUE E,0000,0000,0000,,{Who are these guys?}Kdo jsou ti lidi?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.52,0:11:50.68,Shinsou main,BLUE G,0000,0000,0000,,{They're flying!}Oni lítaj!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.68,0:11:52.61,Shinsou main,KARK,0000,0000,0000,,{Uninvited guests.}Nevítaní hosté.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.61,0:11:53.77,Shinsou main,BLUE F,0000,0000,0000,,Kark Kaburagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.38,0:11:56.65,Shinsou main,KARK,0000,0000,0000,,{Fools.}Hlupáci.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.11,0:12:04.68,Shinsou main,BLUE F,0000,0000,0000,,{Wh-What is this?}C-Co je to?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.07,0:12:07.58,Shinsou main,TSUBAKI,0000,0000,0000,,{Go, Densuke!}Běž, Densuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.97,0:12:17.91,Shinsou main,KOUME,0000,0000,0000,,{Hold it right there!}Zůstaň tam!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.79,0:12:34.21,Shinsou main,TSUBAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Densuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.21,0:12:35.02,Shinsou main,KOTETSU,0000,0000,0000,,{Tsubaki-chan!}Tsubaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.69,0:12:38.94,Shinsou main,TSUBAKI,0000,0000,0000,,{Kotecchan?}Kotíku?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.37,0:12:54.95,Shinsou main,HARU,0000,0000,0000,,{Why, you...}Proč, ty...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.53,0:12:56.54,Shinsou main,AKIRA,0000,0000,0000,,Haru!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.65,0:12:58.46,Shinsou main,HARU,0000,0000,0000,,{Akira?}Akiro?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.91,0:13:00.25,Shinsou main,HARU,0000,0000,0000,,{What are you...}Co ty tu...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.25,0:13:02.21,Shinsou main,AKIRA,0000,0000,0000,,{Haru, stop this.}Haru, přestaň s tím.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.37,0:13:10.18,Shinsou main,HARU,0000,0000,0000,,{I'll kill you for Jun-san!}Zabiju tě pro Juna.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.18,0:13:11.43,Shinsou main,AKIRA,0000,0000,0000,,{Stop, Haru!}Přestaň, Haru!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.12,0:13:16.16,Shinsou main,KARK,0000,0000,0000,,Apasionado.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.18,0:13:37.60,Shinsou main,HARU,0000,0000,0000,,{What?}Cože?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.60,0:13:39.36,Shinsou main,HARU,0000,0000,0000,,{That's not Kamina Chihiro.}To není Kamina Chihiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.96,0:13:44.71,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{Kark!}Karku!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.54,0:13:48.56,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{A single surprise attack.}Prostý překvapivý útok.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.12,0:13:53.18,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{It's the only way to kill Kark before\Nany of the audience members die.}Je to jediný způsob jak zabít Karka předtím než zemře někdo z publika.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.49,0:13:54.52,Shinsou main,AKIRA,0000,0000,0000,,{I'll handle it.}Postarám se o to.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.32,0:13:56.36,Shinsou main,AKIRA,0000,0000,0000,,Elsbernd.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.72,0:14:06.74,Shinsou main,JUN,0000,0000,0000,,{Kamina.}Kamino.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.89,0:14:12.40,Shinsou main,JUN,0000,0000,0000,,{You're mine.}Jsi můj.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.40,0:14:14.25,Shinsou main,JUN,0000,0000,0000,,{I won't let anyone else kill you.}Nenechám nikoho jiného tě zabít.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.16,0:14:17.00,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{Why now?}Proč teď?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.75,0:14:19.22,Shinsou main,KARK,0000,0000,0000,,Aoi Jun.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.71,0:14:21.96,Shinsou main,KARK,0000,0000,0000,,{You're an uninvited guest as well.}Jsi nevítaným hostem.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.17,0:14:26.59,Shinsou main,ARK,0000,0000,0000,,{But I shall allow it for now.}Ale teď to dovolím.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.48,0:14:33.58,Shinsou main,JUN,0000,0000,0000,,{Bastard!}Šmejde!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.93,0:14:36.52,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{I don't have time to fight you!}Nemám čas s tebou bojovat!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.03,0:14:39.02,Shinsou main,JUN,0000,0000,0000,,{I'm going to kill you!}Zabiju tě!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.02,0:14:40.52,Shinsou main,JUN,0000,0000,0000,,{Only me!}Jen já!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.60,0:14:44.13,Shinsou main,JUN,0000,0000,0000,,{Die! Die! Die!}Chcípni! Chcípni! Chcípni!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.13,0:14:45.24,Shinsou main,HARU,0000,0000,0000,,{Jun-san!}June!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.90,0:14:47.11,Shinsou main,TSUBAKI,0000,0000,0000,,{Did Kark...}Co Kark...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.11,0:14:49.75,Shinsou main,SHOKO,0000,0000,0000,,{The plan failed.}Plán selhal.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.28,0:14:53.03,Shinsou main,KARK,0000,0000,0000,,{The concert is at its climax.}Koncert je na svém vrcholu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.37,0:14:56.80,Shinsou main,KARK,0000,0000,0000,,{The sound calls to you from\N the bottom of a deep abyss.}Zvuk volá na vás ze dna hluboké propasti.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.80,0:14:59.68,Shinsou main,KARK,0000,0000,0000,,{Sing, play, and exalt.}Zpívejte, hrajte a oslavujte.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.20,0:15:02.04,Shinsou main,KARK,0000,0000,0000,,{Death has arrived.}Smrt dorazila.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.06,0:15:06.98,Shinsou main,SHOKO,0000,0000,0000,,{This isn't good. This is...}To není dobré. To je...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.98,0:15:07.96,Shinsou main,KOTETSU,0000,0000,0000,,{Chihiro-san!}Chihiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.60,0:15:10.68,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{Don't! Don't do it!}Přestaň! Přestaň s tím!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.97,0:15:14.18,Shinsou main,KARK,0000,0000,0000,,{Death has arrived. Death has arrived.}Smrt dorazila. Smrt dorazila.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.18,0:15:16.14,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{Stop!}Přestaň!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.14,0:15:18.14,Shinsou main,KARK,0000,0000,0000,,{Death has arrived!}Smrt dorazila!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.46,0:15:22.46,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{No...}Ne...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.00,0:15:24.81,Shinsou main,CERDID,0000,0000,0000,,Chihiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.14,0:15:26.93,Shinsou main,JUN,0000,0000,0000,,{That's the face.}Ten výraz.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.93,0:15:30.28,Shinsou main,JUN,0000,0000,0000,,{That's the face twisted with\N despair that I wanted to see.}To je tvář zkroucená zoufalstvím, kterou jsem chtěl vidět.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.04,0:15:34.83,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{I won't give up.}Nevzdám se.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.83,0:15:37.04,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{I promised Inuki-san.}Slíbil jsem to Inuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.04,0:15:40.29,Shinsou main,INUKI,0000,0000,0000,,{As long as you don't give up,\N your wishes will come true.}Dokud se nevzdáš, tvé přání se splní.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.56,0:15:43.17,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{I'm going to save them.}Chystám se je zachránit.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.87,0:15:46.67,Shinsou main,INUKI,0000,0000,0000,,{Show me the future you'll create.}Ukaž mi budoucnost, kterou vytvoříš.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.67,0:15:47.90,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{I can, too!}Taky to dokážu!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.90,0:15:49.36,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{I can do it!}Dokážu to!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.89,0:15:53.55,Shinsou main,JUN,0000,0000,0000,,{Don't be ridiculous!}Nebuď směšnej!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.61,0:15:57.41,Shinsou main,JUN,0000,0000,0000,,{Wh-What?}C-Cože?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.23,0:16:02.39,Shinsou main,KARK,0000,0000,0000,,{Beautiful.}Krása.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.70,0:16:04.00,Shinsou main,KOTETSU,0000,0000,0000,,{Chihiro-san?}Chihiro?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.00,0:16:06.65,Shinsou main,SHOKO,0000,0000,0000,,{Could he be the Lord of Vermilion?}Mohl se stát Vermilionským lordem?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.19,0:16:10.18,Shinsou main,KOTETSU,0000,0000,0000,,{Tsubaki-chan!}Tsubaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.34,0:16:14.39,Shinsou main,KOUME,0000,0000,0000,,{Let's let Chihiro handle this!}Nech Chihira na mě!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.39,0:16:17.24,Shinsou main,KOUME,0000,0000,0000,,{We can't let that thing get outside!}Nemůžeme dopustit, aby se ta věc dostala ven!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.98,0:16:23.39,Shinsou main,JUN,0000,0000,0000,,{Damn it!}Sakra.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.26,0:16:29.59,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{Inuki-san trusted me to\Ncarry out his dying wish!}Inuki mi věřil, že se postarám o jeho poslední přání!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.99,0:16:33.88,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{So I'll never give up!}Takže se nikdy nevzdám!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.39,0:16:36.36,Shinsou main,JUN,0000,0000,0000,,{Y-You...}T-Ty...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.05,0:16:38.85,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{You won't beat me!}Neporazíš mě!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.92,0:16:43.10,Shinsou main,JUN,0000,0000,0000,,{It's no use. I can't win.}To nebude fungovat. Nemůžu vyhrát.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.45,0:16:49.11,Shinsou main,JUN,0000,0000,0000,,{I couldn't even stop you.\NOf course I don't stand a chance.}Nemohl jsem tě dokonce ani zastavit. Samozřejmě, že nemám šanci.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.74,0:16:52.32,Shinsou main,JUN,0000,0000,0000,,{Is that why you chose him?}Proto jsis ho vybral?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.04,0:16:56.28,Shinsou main,KARK,0000,0000,0000,,{Fool.}Hlupák.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.69,0:16:59.61,Shinsou main,KARK,0000,0000,0000,,{The source of the blood armaments'\N power is in their very name.}Zdrojem síly krevní výzbroje je právě v jejich jménu.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.61,0:17:02.04,Shinsou main,KARK,0000,0000,0000,,{Use too much, and you'll die of blood loss.}Používej ho moc a zemřeš na ztrátu krve.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.77,0:17:05.92,Shinsou main,JUN,0000,0000,0000,,{Is this how it ends?}Takhle to skončí?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.67,0:17:13.00,Shinsou main,JUN,0000,0000,0000,,{You're mine!}Jsi můj!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.11,0:17:19.10,Shinsou main,KARK,0000,0000,0000,,Bravo.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.10,0:17:22.81,Shinsou main,KARK,0000,0000,0000,,{You successfully drew out the\N qualities of the Lord of Vermilion.}Uspěšně jsi vytáhl kvality Vermilionského lorda.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.17,0:17:27.86,Shinsou main,KARK,0000,0000,0000,,{But I'm not so generous that\N I'd so easily let you take his head.}Ale nejsem tak štědrý, že bych tě tak snadno nechal vzít jeho hlavu.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.78,0:17:32.31,Shinsou main,KARK,0000,0000,0000,,Sipario.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.53,0:17:39.12,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Aoi Jun...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.38,0:17:43.33,Shinsou main,KARK,0000,0000,0000,,{The more wretchedly painted,}Čím nešťastněji namalované,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.84,0:17:47.35,Shinsou main,KARK,0000,0000,0000,,{the more beautiful the death.}tím krásnější smrt.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.34,0:17:50.71,Shinsou main,HARU,0000,0000,0000,,{You killed Jun-san!}Zabil jsi Juna!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.29,0:17:53.59,Shinsou main,KARK,0000,0000,0000,,{I shall paint you, too.}Namaluju tě taky.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.76,0:17:57.79,Shinsou main,HARU,0000,0000,0000,,{Akira...}Akiro...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.61,0:18:00.65,Shinsou main,AKIRA,0000,0000,0000,,Haru...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.51,0:18:03.85,Shinsou main,HARU,0000,0000,0000,,{Why are you...}Proč jsi...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.85,0:18:07.42,Shinsou main,KARK,0000,0000,0000,,{It is truly beautiful to see\Nsomeone sacrifice themselves}Je skutečně krásné vidět, že se někdo obětuje sám
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.42,0:18:09.73,Shinsou main,KARK,0000,0000,0000,,{to save the one they love.}pro záchranu někoho koho miluje.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.73,0:18:10.98,Shinsou main,KARK,0000,0000,0000,,{However...}Nicméně...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.78,0:18:15.97,Shinsou main,KARK,0000,0000,0000,,{It is even more beautiful\N when that turns to despair.}Je to ještě krásnější, když se to změní v zoufalství.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.01,0:18:17.99,Shinsou main,AKIRA,0000,0000,0000,,{No...}Ne...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.04,0:18:25.25,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{Kark...}Karku...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.42,0:18:31.08,Shinsou main,KARK,0000,0000,0000,,Kamina Chihiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.49,0:18:35.28,Shinsou main,KARK,0000,0000,0000,,{The man who may have\N become the Lord of Vermilion.}Muž, který se mohl stát Vermilionským lordem.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.28,0:18:39.62,Shinsou main,KARK,0000,0000,0000,,{Regrettably, you heard my requiem.}Bohužel jsi slyšel mou pohřební píseň.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.62,0:18:46.22,Shinsou main,KARK,0000,0000,0000,,{Now die. Your soul has been\N purified to black by my melody.}Nyní zemři. Tvá duše byla očištěná na černo mou melodií.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.98,0:18:48.48,Shinsou main,KARK,0000,0000,0000,,{Death has arrived.}Smrt dorazila.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.70,0:18:56.30,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{How can you toy with human\N lives, Kark Kaburagi?}Jak jsi můžeš hrát s lidskými životy, Kaburagi Karku?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.33,0:19:00.28,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{You won't get away with this.}Já ti neodpustím.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.96,0:19:04.05,Shinsou main,KOTETSU,0000,0000,0000,,{Chihiro-san?}Chihiro?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.84,0:19:07.29,Shinsou main,KOUME,0000,0000,0000,,{No, that's not Chihiro.}Ne, to není Chihiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.06,0:19:12.49,Shinsou main,TSUBAKI,0000,0000,0000,,{The Lord of Vermilion.}Vermilionský lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.08,0:19:17.80,Shinsou main,KARK,0000,0000,0000,,{Come, Kamina Chihiro.}Pojď, Kamina Chihiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.26,0:19:20.72,Shinsou main,KARK,0000,0000,0000,,Ahura Mazda.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.41,0:19:27.31,Shinsou main,KOTETSU,0000,0000,0000,,{I-Incredible.}N-Neuvěřitelné.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.85,0:19:34.48,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{I hesitated to stain my hands with blood.}Váhal jsem si zašpinit ruce krví.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.97,0:19:40.15,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{But not anymore.}Ale teď už ne.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.53,0:19:46.66,Shinsou main,KARK,0000,0000,0000,,{Haven't you forgotten to whom\N Azura Mazda's cry belongs?}Nezapomněli jste, komu patří křik Azura Mazdy?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.82,0:19:50.62,Shinsou main,KARK,0000,0000,0000,,{That's right. It's my fans.}Tak je to správně. Jsou to mí fanoušci.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.62,0:19:54.67,Shinsou main,KARK,0000,0000,0000,,{Can you kill thousands of lives?}Dokážeš zabít tisíce životů?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.41,0:19:57.59,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{They aren't turning back now.}Nemůžou být proměněni zpět.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.59,0:20:02.18,Shinsou main,KARK,0000,0000,0000,,{Are you sure? It may be possible.}Jsi si jistý? Možná to možné je.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.88,0:20:05.93,Shinsou main,KARK,0000,0000,0000,,{And if it is, you can't kill me.}A proto mě nemůžeš zabít.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.44,0:20:09.58,Shinsou main,KOTETSU,0000,0000,0000,,{Chihiro-san!}Chihiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.58,0:20:10.77,Shinsou main,KOUME,0000,0000,0000,,Chihiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.54,0:20:14.15,Shinsou main,KARK,0000,0000,0000,,{People are truly weak.}Lidé jsou skutečně slabí.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.15,0:20:18.04,Shinsou main,KARK,0000,0000,0000,,{They cling to the faintest\N hope and fall into despair.}Přitisknou se k nejslabší naději a padnou do zoufalství.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.20,0:20:21.68,Shinsou main,KARK,0000,0000,0000,,{Their only comfort is death.}Jejich jedinou útěchou je smrt.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.40,0:20:23.73,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{I can kill you.}Můžu tě zabít.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.48,0:20:27.70,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{If staining my hands with blood is the\N path to becoming the Lord of Vermilion,}Jestliže si musím zašpinit ruce krví, abych se stal Vermilionským lordem,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.70,0:20:29.12,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{so be it.}tak budiž.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.39,0:20:32.29,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{I don't care if I won't be forgiven.}Je mi jedno, jestli mi nebude odpuštěno.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.29,0:20:34.00,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{I'll bear that burden!}Ponesu tu zátěž!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.05,0:20:45.31,Shinsou main,KARK,0000,0000,0000,,{You're stronger than I expected.}Jsi silnější, než jsem čekal.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.31,0:20:47.81,Shinsou main,KARK,0000,0000,0000,,{You truly are supreme.}Skutečně jsi překvapil.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.80,0:20:55.29,Shinsou main,SHOKO,0000,0000,0000,,{The greatest achievement was mine.}Největší úspěch byl můj.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.29,0:20:58.26,Shinsou main,SHOKO,0000,0000,0000,,{Did you see that, Dux-sama?}Vidíte to, paní Dux?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.72,0:21:00.14,Shinsou main,SHOKO,0000,0000,0000,,{Truly, I am...}Skutečně, jsem...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.33,0:21:03.40,Shinsou main,KARK,0000,0000,0000,,{This is the end.}Tohle je konec.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.77,0:21:05.16,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{Kark!}Karku!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.70,0:21:07.69,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{Where are you?}Kde jsi?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.14,0:21:11.01,Shinsou main,KARK,0000,0000,0000,,{I'd like to see the world you create,}Rád bych viděl svět, který stvoříš,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.01,0:21:14.62,Shinsou main,KARK,0000,0000,0000,,{but granting you death is the greater joy.}ale poskytnout ti smrt je větší potěšení.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.33,0:21:18.23,Shinsou main,KARK,0000,0000,0000,,{You won't want to miss the encore.}Nenechte si ujít přídavek.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.88,0:21:25.90,Shinsou main,GRUMMAN,0000,0000,0000,,{We can't cause another Great Collapse anymore.}Nemůžeme způsobit další Velké zhroucení.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.37,0:21:27.64,Shinsou main,GRUMMAN,0000,0000,0000,,{What should we do?}Co bychom měli dělat?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.26,0:21:30.44,Shinsou main,GRUMMAN,0000,0000,0000,,{Help me, Chiyu.}Pomoz mi, Chiyu.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.66,0:21:33.99,Shinsou main,CHIYU,0000,0000,0000,,{Yes, Father.}Ano, otče.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.99,0:21:35.16,Shinsou main,GRUMMAN,0000,0000,0000,,{Thank you.}Děkuji ti.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.17,0:21:39.09,Shinsou main,GRUMMAN,0000,0000,0000,,{Thank you, Mitsuki.}Děkuji ti, Mitsuki.
